artners llp a private equity fund specializing in growth stage online media and marketing businesses   from  to  ljung was ceo of siguiente capital ab a small venture capital investment firm focused on it and telecom innovation  from  through  he was head analyst online investments for that firm    mr ljung has a masters degree in management from university of st andrews uk  he has studied at the lubin school of business and the universite de la sorbonne  ralph and henrik are vital new additions to our board at a time when the company is moving to the next level of our business plan remarked odysseys ceo john foster  we are already benefiting greatly from their collective expertise in production and finance about odyssey pictures corporation  initially an entertainment company focusing on financing and distribution of first run feature films odyssey has adapted its business model to become a diversified mediamarketing services company  the companys lines of business now encompass producers representation branding  marketing and iptv digital delivery technologies  odysseys producers representative service provides an extensive suite of sales and marketing services to independent filmmakers seeking to gain traction in the international distribution and rights markets  these services include international sales contract negotiation marketing materials strategic planning and completion financing httpodysseypixcom forwardlooking statements  certain statements contained herein are forward looking these forwardlooking statements are based on our current expectations and are subject to a number of risks uncertainties and assumptions many factors could cause actual results to differ significantly from these statements including our history of operating losses our need for additional financing a failure of our products to perform as expected introduction of competing products by other companies pressure on prices from competitors andor customers regulatory obstacles to new pr