ip with siguiente since  which has led to siguiente becoming a significant financial resource for odyssey odyssey will be exhibiting at two locations palais niveau  –  at the palais des festivals which is the center of the film market and the main screening area for the film festival as well as at riviera h a large and well appointed ‘producer’s booth’ the company is cohosting with strategic partner veland films to provide a forum for film producers to present international coproduction projects odyssey will be actively looking to make content acquisitions and licensing deals to add to odyssey’s growing library of children’s and general interest programming siguiente will be working closely with odyssey to review and analyze specific terms regarding any potential involvement by odyssey in coproduction and international licensing and rights acquisition deals “we are excited about our increased presence at cannes this year” states odyssey’s presidentceo john foster “in addition to taking booths we will be fully staffed and plan to be very active in the buying and selling of content rights siguiente’s financial counsel will be very helpful in that respect” about odyssey  odyssey pictures corporation was founded in  as a publicly traded entertainment company specializing in the financing and distribution of motion pictures texas based odyssey has restrategized over the past two years and adopted a more diversified business model including branding and marketing services targeting key clients in ecommerce search engine positioning and online lead generation the company is also engaged in content acquisition multiplatform distribution new media technology and corporate finance about siguiente capital  siguiente capital accelerates enterprises by allocating effective and powerful corporate finance and structuring services based in stockholm sweden the firm’s investment scope is predominantly focused on europe and north america but with advances being made in asia as well most of siguiente’s clients are in a changeintensive stage mainly operating in growth sectors such as it ecommerce and telecom as the name implies siguiente supports ventures and individuals that are creating the next significant technologies and businesses about the cannes film market marché du film  the marché du film is an international crossroads for the cinema industry as a major meeting place for professionals each year the marché du film gathers buyers distributors and producers for ten days dedicated to meetings and negotiations this unique international event allows all professionals to develop their projects present their latest news establish partnerships and coproductions forward looking statements  certain statements contained herein are forward looking these forwardlooking statements are based on our current expectations and are subject to a number of risks uncertainties and assumptions many factors could cause actual results to differ significantly from these statements including our history of operating losses our need for additional financing a failure of our products to perform as expected introduction of competing products by other companies pressures on prices from competitors andor customers regulatory obstacles to new product introductions lack of acceptance of our products and technology changes these risks uncertainties and assumptions are detailed in documents filed by us with the securities and exchange commission the company cautions that the foregoing list of important factors is not exclusive any forwardlooking statements are made as of the date of the document in which they appear the company does not undertake to update any forwardlooking statement that may be made from time to time by or on behalf of the company media and investor relations contact dan spelling at spelling communications   share article on socal media or email view article via pdf print contact author dan spelling  email  visit website news center  facebook facebook   